			<table class="t218__blocktable" style="height:100vh;background-color:#eeeff2;" data-height-correct-vh="yes">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td class="t218__blocktext">
							<div class="t218__textwrapper">
								<div class="t218__descrfield t-descr t-descr_xxxl" style=" color:#2d3338;" field="title">
									<div style="font-size:40px;" data-customstyle="yes"><strong><span data-redactor-tag="span" style="font-weight: 600;">About us</span></strong><br></div>
								</div>
								<div class="t218__textfield t-text t-text_md" style=" color:#2d3338;" field="text">
									<div style="font-size:18px;" data-customstyle="yes">Retreat House Narbuli is&nbsp;a&nbsp;modern spacious cottage, which is&nbsp;located in&nbsp;the most unique village in&nbsp;Latvia&nbsp;— Amatciems, 80&nbsp;km from Riga&nbsp;— the capital of&nbsp;Latvia. <br><br>There are no&nbsp;fences here and very few street lamps, the houses are quite far from each other having their own «intimate» space, hidden from others by&nbsp;picturesque hills and trees. Nature literally embraces you here&nbsp;— roe deer, deer and foxes often come to&nbsp;the House. And, most importantly, it&nbsp;is&nbsp;very quiet here. <br><br>Around the House, which has its own access to&nbsp;the water, you will find many walking trails and places for your retreat. No&nbsp;matter what inner intention you come with, the space itself conforms to&nbsp;you and helps you achieve these goals.<br></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</td>
						<td class="t218__blockimg t-bgimg loaded" data-original="http://retreatlatvia/wp-content/uploads/tilda/537641/pages/27234823/tild6236-3062-4463-b665-333762316264__img_8425.jpeg" bgimgfiled="img" style="background-image: url(&quot;http://retreatlatvia/wp-content/uploads/tilda/537641/pages/27234823/tild6236-3062-4463-b665-333762316264__img_8425.jpeg&quot;);" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject" data-lazy-rule="comm:resize,round:100">
							<meta itemprop="image" content="http://retreatlatvia/wp-content/uploads/tilda/537641/pages/27234823/tild6236-3062-4463-b665-333762316264__img_8425.jpeg">
						</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</div>
	</div>
